{"bookId": "67656d13c83ed0673b8b7b68", "moduleId": "67656d13c83ed0673b8b7b68", "subjectId": "67656d19c83ed0673b8b7b75", "chapterId": "67656d19c83ed0673b8b7b77", "subject": "Mathematics", "chapter": "Miscellaneous Mathematics", "count": 2, "questions": [{"id": 0, "subject": "Mathematics", "chapter": "Miscellaneous Mathematics", "exam": "Engineering", "examName": "Top 250 Single Correct Qs of JEE Main 2023-2020", "q": "<p>If for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mfrac><mi>&#960;</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mfenced><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>,&nbsp;then the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>n</mi></math> is equal to :&nbsp;</p>", "options": ["<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>20</mn></math>", "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>12</mn></math>", "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>9</mn></math>", "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>16</mn></math>"], "answer": 1, "solution": "<p>Given&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mfrac><mi>&#960;</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>.</mo><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>.</mo><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>10</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>.</mo><mo>.</mo><mo>.</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>)</mo></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mfenced><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><msqrt><mi>n</mi></msqrt><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><msqrt><mi>n</mi></msqrt><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>log</mi><mn>10</mn></msub><msqrt><mn>10</mn></msqrt></mrow></mfenced></msup><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mi>n</mi><mn>10</mn></mfrac></msqrt></math></p><p>By squaring we get,&nbsp;</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>sin</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>cos</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>n</mi><mn>10</mn></mfrac></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>sin</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>.</mo><mi>cos</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>n</mi><mn>10</mn></mfrac></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>n</mi><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></math></p>", "difficulty": "Easy", "source": "JEE Main 2021 (16 Mar Shift 1)", "_marksId": "648b5a69417cc3fb48d66ea9"}, {"id": 0, "subject": "Mathematics", "chapter": "Miscellaneous Mathematics", "exam": "Engineering", "examName": "Top 250 Single Correct Qs of JEE Main 2023-2020", "q": "Let <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>:</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>&#8805;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mi>Z</mi><mo>:</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>&#8804;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>. Then the number of elements in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>S</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>T</mi></math> is", "options": ["<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>7</mn></math>", "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>5</mn></math>", "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn></math>", "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn></math>"], "answer": 3, "solution": "<blockquote><p>Given,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mfenced close=\"|\" open=\"|\"><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><mfenced close=\"|\" open=\"|\"><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>&#8804;</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mfenced close=\"|\" open=\"|\"><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>&#8804;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>7</mn><mo>&#177;</mo><msqrt><mn>13</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mfenced close=\"|\" open=\"|\"><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>&#8712;</mo><mfenced close=\"]\" open=\"[\"><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>7</mn><mo>-</mo><msqrt><mn>13</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>7</mn><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mn>13</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p>Also given&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mtext>Integers</mtext></math>, so&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp;can be&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#177;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#177;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#177;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#177;</mo><mn>5</mn></math></p><p>Now out of these values of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp;only&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></math>&nbsp;will satisfy&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfenced close=\"|\" open=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mfenced close=\"|\" open=\"|\"><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>&#8805;</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p><p>So,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>S</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>T</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mfenced close=\"}\" open=\"{\"><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p>So,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>n</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>T</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math></p></blockquote>", "difficulty": "Easy", "source": "JEE Main 2022 (28 Jul Shift 2)", "_marksId": "648b5a6d417cc3fb48d67cb5"}]}